bulldust
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:euphemism for <i>bullshit</i> lies, rot, nonsense; boasting - as a noun or as an exclam. (<i>Bullswool </i> is another variant; the politest is the innocuous Bovril; cf. also bull, heifer dust).


